{"type": "article", "id": 27226, "title": "台湾这个牙科诊所，想用清新的环境打消患者的恐惧", "description": "如起居室一般的候诊室，看上去真的有能够让人放松的魔力。", "date": "2016-05-24T06:50:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 19064, "name": "诊所设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 219, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164533N1q8zFnLKE5jYCiJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>据说现在有种病叫“牙科恐惧症”（dental fear），不管是治疗前还是治疗期间的那种紧张、焦虑、恐惧，几乎是不可控的。</p>\n<p>不管是医学手段还是心理学指导，各领域都已经在积极应对这种病症了。而换到设计师层面，他们能做的，也就是尽力通过设计手段来创造一间“不再惧怕来看病”的牙科诊所。</p>\n<p>去年我们曾介绍过东京一家温暖如面包店般的牙科诊所。最近，在台湾桃园市，比利时建筑师 Germain Canon 也抱着打消患者内心恐惧的念头，设计了一间温馨如家般的牙科诊所“楽心牙医”。</p>\n<p>Germain Canon 平日住在台北，同时他也是一名摄影师和插画师，<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/05/22/germain-canon-dental-clinic-taoyuan-city-taiwan-patients-less-afraid-living-room/\">“我的目标就是想设计一间让患者不再害怕去看病的诊所。”</a></p>\n<p>整个诊所都沿街布局，这就使得走廊相连的诊疗室和候诊室都能充分享受到自然采光的优势。磨砂玻璃和滑动门承担了创造不同功能分区的功能，也一定程度上创造了诊所整体空间在视觉上的联系和延伸。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164526vGhy8CdPl0LfmAxr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164527BOWC2sT7JI03PKz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164527rOM1xaW9RpBVT4oj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">与前述提到的东京那家诊所运用大面积木质门窗的想法相似，Germain Canon 也用了大量木材和玻璃元素，烘托出温暖氛围的同时，他还想借由这些材料传递一些<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/05/22/germain-canon-dental-clinic-taoyuan-city-taiwan-patients-less-afraid-living-room/\">“小小的惊喜感”</a>。诊所外部大面积落地窗与浅色窗帘的组合，在灯光的烘托下透着一股静谧的安全感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164528d0lNf8JieYOxs7jp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164528wKRH4zvOuLeUmb72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164529aZd6pXoEgj2fGNkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>尤其是候诊室的设计，乍一看就像是个家里的起居空间，原木色的木质地板搭配暖色系沙发、灰色软垫座椅以及木质桌椅、搁架等，中心区域围绕着茶几的地垫更是给人一种家人团聚围坐在一起的感觉。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164529YmnaqBz5VgTF7Q9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164530DvK8GNazIpCeqZU6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>半透明的玻璃隔绝出矩形的封闭档案室，亦成为分隔诊疗室和公共空间的隔断。此外，Germain Canon 还专门辟出一块小空间，用来给患者在诊疗前后拍摄照片用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164530A9NOxMJIKjLDnQuB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164531z6wqhkUjWPoAHp9X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164531UuT3KbXmWCgHEGio.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>浴室也是一处特别的空间，颜色对比分明的锯齿状花纹显出轻快活泼的气息，墙面上带有凹槽的木质搁架用来存储患者的牙刷与牙膏，这也是牙科诊所独有的特色吧。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164532hz8qZ5rwOApWFlsS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164532ghSJG7lPwuLUra8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/05/22/germain-canon-dental-clinic-taoyuan-city-taiwan-patients-less-afraid-living-room/\">Dezeen </a>  摄影：Germain Canon</p>\n\n"}